{"id":5852,"date":"2024-01-09T16:03:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-09T10:33:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=5852"},"modified":"2024-08-02T13:50:24","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T08:20:24","slug":"interior-designs-for-hall","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/hall-interiors\/interior-designs-for-hall\/","title":{"rendered":"Elegant and Classy Hall Interior Design Ideas You&#8217;ll Love"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Your hall is the most lived-in room of your home &#8211; design it well to create a fabulous first impression. We spend a lot of time in our halls or living room. This space needs to look elegant, functional and comfortable for family members, relatives or guests. Blending everything together and matching it to be perfect can be tricky. But that is where we come in. So, here are some<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\"> interior designs for your hall<\/a> you will want to steal. Keep reading for beautiful, stylish and simple interior designs for halls of any size.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple Interior Hall Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When we say simple we do not imply designing your hall with plain and unattractive interiors. If space is an issue, every inch of your floor and walls must be utilised well into the interior design of your hall. A combination of wooden flooring, artificial lighting and minimalistic furniture will make your hall look expensive.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005331\/interior-design-for-hall-for-home.jpg\" alt=\"Interior design for hall where every inch of your floor and walls must be utilised in living hall design in simple\" class=\"wp-image-5859\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005331\/interior-design-for-hall-for-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005331\/interior-design-for-hall-for-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005331\/interior-design-for-hall-for-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005331\/interior-design-for-hall-for-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A minimalistic hall can be stylish and efficient with carefully chosen designs and materials.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Sleek TV Unit Design For Hall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This sleek TV unit is a perfect fit for lounge or family rooms. This type of unit is easy to fit into any area and occupies less space &#8211; no guesses why they are a hot trend in apartment complexes. Bring in some LED strip lighting to brighten up your living room without going over the edge. In this unit we see a basic low lying cabinet that is great to store books, DVDs, CD players or any other small items.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005339\/tv-unit-design-for-hall-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"Hall interior design which has a sleek TV unit which is a perfect fit for lounge\" class=\"wp-image-5861\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005339\/tv-unit-design-for-hall-interior-design.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005339\/tv-unit-design-for-hall-interior-design-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005339\/tv-unit-design-for-hall-interior-design-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005339\/tv-unit-design-for-hall-interior-design-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Mount your TV on the wall over an unattached cabinet for a clean sleek look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Looking to enliven your living room's interior designs?\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/08173628\/looking-to-enliven-your-living-rooms-interior-designs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bring Fun To The Floor Of Your Hall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If your living room is styled with neutral palettes and enough artefacts it&#8217;s time to bring some spark to your flooring. Bright carpets or wooden flooring with patterns lends timeless elegance and a luxurious feel hall interiors. Smooth, polished, and topped with an artisan rug or a carpet, your floors will now look aesthetically pleasing.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005328\/home-hall-design-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Hall interior design styled with neutral palettes and artefacts\" class=\"wp-image-5858\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005328\/home-hall-design-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005328\/home-hall-design-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005328\/home-hall-design-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005328\/home-hall-design-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Add a coloured rug will increase the style quotient of your hall interiors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"474\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/17185944\/hall-interior-design-dos-donts-474x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Hall interior design do's and don'ts - best practices for stylish and functional hallways\" class=\"wp-image-51678\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/17185944\/hall-interior-design-dos-donts-474x1024.jpg 474w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/17185944\/hall-interior-design-dos-donts-139x300.jpg 139w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/17185944\/hall-interior-design-dos-donts-768x1661.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/17185944\/hall-interior-design-dos-donts-710x1536.jpg 710w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/17185944\/hall-interior-design-dos-donts-150x324.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/17185944\/hall-interior-design-dos-donts.jpg 941w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cupboards In Your Living Room Hall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now if you have a large hall or live in a studio apartment you can accommodate a closet. While this may be an atypical choice for some, closets in your living can add a great amount of style. It offers you more storage space be it for extra clothes, linen or crockery -stuff that you do not need everyday. A cupboard in your hall is particularly useful when you have lots of guests at home and need additional items.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005311\/cupboard-design-for-hall-for-your-home.jpg\" alt=\"Hall interior design with cupboards which offers storage pace for extra clothes\" class=\"wp-image-5854\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005311\/cupboard-design-for-hall-for-your-home.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005311\/cupboard-design-for-hall-for-your-home-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005311\/cupboard-design-for-hall-for-your-home-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005311\/cupboard-design-for-hall-for-your-home-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A cupboard in your hall will solve problems you didn\u2019t know you had<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Walls Matter In Your Living Hall Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Your hall is complete and you\u2019ve added furniture, lighting and decor but what about your walls? Walls play an integral role to give your hall interiors a complete look. Opt for a decorative wall hanging to bring in character and visual interest to your hall. You can also use tiles or wallpaper on the walls to balance spruce it up a bit. A light wooden panelled wall combined with a classic carpet and a brightly colourful sofa will change the vibe of your hall interiors completely. If your hall has a place for a mantle then a large sized mirror is a stunning addition for a bold look.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005342\/wall-painting-designs-for-hall.jpg\" alt=\"Hall interior design with proper lighting and decor\" class=\"wp-image-5862\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005342\/wall-painting-designs-for-hall.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005342\/wall-painting-designs-for-hall-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005342\/wall-painting-designs-for-hall-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/21005342\/wall-painting-designs-for-hall-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Complete the look of your hall interiors with innovative ideas, DIY and eclectic decor<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Good hall interior design is harmonious, elegant and makes for a space where you can relax and entertain your guests, unwind after work or be used as a dining space by incorporating a partition. If you need help or inspiration to design your hall interiors our team of expert designers from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> can help you. Do Visit us or leave your comments in the section below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/hall-interiors\/latest-false-ceiling-designs-for-hall\/\">Latest false ceiling designs for hall<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/hall-interiors\/colour-combination-for-hall\/\">Best colour combination for hall<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/hall-interiors\/hall-furniture-design-ideas\/\">Hall furniture design ideas<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Personalised Dream Home Interiors<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space on home interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"label